# Voice Workroom — Session Handoff 2026-07-12

Continuation surface for the **JoelClaw Voice Workroom** effort. The map is truth: [`.brain/projects/wayfinder/joelclaw-voice-workroom-map.svx`](./wayfinder/joelclaw-voice-workroom-map.svx) — read it (and the wayfinder skill at `/Users/joel/.agents/skills/wayfinder/SKILL.md`) before doing anything.

## Current objective

Work the map's frontier, one ticket per session. The destination: phone-in ShitRat bound to pi-discord-threads sessions and wayfinder tracker state — resumable as voice or text, recallable, discoverable across products.

## Live state (all verified working 2026-07-11 night)

- **Dial tone both directions** on `+1 360 389 4321`. Inbound: Telnyx FQDN connection → `3u3nhn7qkku.sip.livekit.cloud` (TCP) → trunk `ST_sp5bRD9369Di` → dispatch `SDR_NqfyvnCWAA7j` → worker. Outbound: trunk `ST_KAQ9ZS6xW6Fo` → `sip.telnyx.com` (credential auth).
- **Worker**: `com.joel.voice-agent` user LaunchAgent on flagg, `~/Code/joelhooks/joelclaw/infra/voice-agent/main.py`, logs `~/.local/log/voice-agent.{log,err}`. Restart: `launchctl kickstart -k gui/501/com.joel.voice-agent` — **drops live calls** (no graceful drain; known gap).
- **Persona**: ShitRat (from shitrat-cli defaults — sharp, loyal, skeptical, receipt-first), Tom Australian voice (`DYkrAHD8iwork3YSUBbs`), 1.2x speed, terse Joel-style (one sentence default — kid-QA'd). Local config: `~/.config/joelclaw/voice-agent.yaml` (PII, not in git; allowlist = Joel's cell only).
- **Tools live**: open_loops + loop_detail (wiki edition via `127.0.0.1:8790/latest.json`), recall (Typesense), slack_search/slack_thread/slack_reply (Joel's user token, replies post AS Joel, verbal confirm required), calendar/tasks/health/voice-switching (pre-existing).
- **Guest mode**: unknown callers get a bare agent — zero tools, zero private context, 10-min cap, transcripts quarantined to `voice/guests/` and NEVER sent to the memory pipeline (injection containment). No caller ID → fail-closed hangup.
- **Fleet calling**: `call-joel "reason"` (flagg, `~/.local/bin`) rings Joel; ShitRat opens with the reason (via `call_reason` participant attribute). Fleet skill pushed: dark-wizard `skills/call-joel/SKILL.md`.
- **Noise**: Krisp BVCTelephony on every session; barge-in needs 0.8s + 2 words; knobs in local config `audio:` section.

